      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in surrogate validation match those specified in the COU for the intended CPB operating environment.",
      "rationale": "Blood properties (viscosity 3.5 mPa·s, density 1060 kg/m³ at 37°C), pump geometry nominal dimensions, and flow-speed combinations in the validation dataset are consistent with the COU specification for CPB operation. No discrepancy between validation inputs and COU-specified inputs was identified for the nominal operating conditions evaluated."
    }
