    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The ML surrogate for hemolysis prediction satisfies all seven assessed credibility factors at or above required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Test-set performance (MAE=0.031, R²=0.974) meets the acceptance criterion for output comparison. The surrogate correctly identifies worst-case RH operating conditions across the nominal flow-speed design space. All assessed factors are compliant; six factors are not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. The assessment team concluded that the surrogate provides sufficient credibility for the COU decision of identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
